item.title: Prologue
item.description: Why Now my notes are all collected through Notion, I highly recommend it. But I think it may be also good to publish my notes somewhere 1. just in case 2. someone may find it helpful 3. Because I want to? Who Anyone? Leave me your comments. What I guess it will be mainly technical notes for now, I haven’t given a lot of thoughts of what to journal yet. So yeah, it’s random stuff.
